org.bukkit.permissions

Interface Permissible

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ServerOperator
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BlockCommandSender, CommandMinecart, CommandSender, ConsoleCommandSender, HumanEntity, Player, RemoteConsoleCommandSender
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PermissibleBase, PoreBlockCommandSender, PoreCommandMinecart, PoreCommandSender, PoreConsoleCommandSender, PoreHumanEntity, PorePermissible, PorePermissibleBase, PorePlayer, PoreRemoteConsoleCommandSender, PoreServerCommandSender

    public interface Permissible
extends ServerOperator
    Represents an object that may be assigned permissions
